Automated User Account Lockout (Suspicious Login)

### Flow (ASCII Diagram)

+-------------------------+
| SIEM Alert: Suspicious  |
| Login (geo impossible)  |
+-------------------------+
           |
           v
+-------------------------+
| Enrich w/ Geo & TI Feeds|
+-------------------------+
           |
           v
+-------------------------+
| Check Recent Logins     |
| & MFA Failures          |
+-------------------------+
           |
           v
+-------------------------+
| Auto-Disable Account    |
| (via AD/Azure AD API)   |
+-------------------------+
           |
           v
+-------------------------+
| Notify SOC + User       |
+-------------------------+

**Benefit:** prevents account misuse within 1â€“2 minutes of detection, instead of waiting for manual SOC approval.
